must be documented with a verifiable source.","classification_options":["Improving","Stable","Declining","Market-Dependent"],"min_rationale_chars":20}'::jsonb,
  '{"factors":{"abs":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"Rose from 4.8 to 10.4 months - deep buyer''s market territory. For-sale exit conditions are severely unfavorable."},"dom":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"Rose from 34 to 58 days - a 71% increase confirming materially weakening buyer demand."},"lts":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"93.8% - buyers negotiating significant concessions well below asking price."},"msp":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"-4.0% actual price decline. Exit value is eroding and must be reflected in the investment analysis."},"inv":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"Nearly doubled from 12 to 19 actives - rising unsold inventory compounds the unfavorable exit picture."},"rvr":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"Nearly doubled from 6.2% to 11.8% - rental demand deteriorating alongside for-sale demand. Both the exit and the income paths are weakening simultaneously."},"emp":{"present":true,"classification":"Declining","rationale":"340-position reduction with expected secondary wave effects is a documented, verifiable external demand shock that must be cited with a specific source."},"sea":{"present":false,"rationale":"No seasonal data was provided. This is a distractor."},"new":{"present":false,"rationale":"No new construction data was provided. This is a distractor."}}}'::jsonb
FROM scenarios s
