ces market rent trend and rental vacancy as parallel investor indicators. When both for-sale and rental markets are transitioning negatively together, the case for continued hold weakens. The new apartment supply factor requires Market-Dependent because its full impact on market rent has not yet resolved.","classification_options":["Improving","Stable","Declining","Market-Dependent"],"min_rationale_chars":20}'::jsonb,
