n the corridor - a documented, project-specific declining factor."},"post":{"present":false,"rationale":"CRITICAL DISTRACTOR: Post-taking and post-construction data is inadmissible. The analysis must be confined to conditions as of the date of taking."},"sea":{"present":false,"rationale":"No seasonal data was provided. This is a distractor."}}}'::jsonb
