s should not appear in the market condition indicator analysis."},"gm_ctrl":{"present":false,"rationale":"METHODOLOGICAL DISTRACTOR: The flood zone submarket is the correct controlling market area for FHA analysis of this property. Using the strong general market would produce an incorrect Increasing designation that misrepresents conditions for flood zone buyers."},"sea":{"present":false,"rationale":"No seasonal data was provided. This is a distractor."}}}'::jsonb
